reviewText: it was a suggested that I watch a show in spanish I was told by someone that is how they learned english. Well I am still not fluent in spanish but I learned enough that I could follow along with the storyline.I loved this novella I  watched it everyday on univision. I would dicuss the show with my spanish speaking co workers.If I am correct the other review said this novella was bad. Maybe it's  a good thing I am  not fluent in spanish because to me this novella was better than most american soaps.
summary: I started watching this to see if I could improve my spanish

reviewText: En general el Resumen Es Bueno solo que Se Omitieron Escenas Muy Importantes como el asesinato de Cecilia, la muerte del Catrin, la muerte de Tobias y de Libertad y el Raton.Tampoco se ve la muerte de Fabio cuando tiene el supuesto accidente, no se ve cuando muere envenenada Lucila ni lo que pasa con el padre de Ana Cristina, Rogelio Valencia.Como era de esperarse al ser una Edición vieja no contiene el Tema Principal de la Telenovela, tiene otro que nada que ver pero en gral el Dvd es bueno.
